title: Brigador (Early Access)
description:
About This Game
Great Leader is dead. You have one night to liberate Solo Nobre.

Brigador is an isometric vehicular action game. Choose the right vehicle and weapons to suit your play style, and face off against the occupying factions. Discover tactics and unlock new vehicles and weapons as you clear the city... or die trying.

Then do it all over again.

Features

    Choose from many different mechs, tanks, and antigrav vehicles to pilot.
    Blast your way through completely destructible environments.
    Wide range of weapons available for different play styles.
    9 high detail, pre-authored levels with more to come.
    Short, high intensity playthroughs against randomized faction & enemy spawning: every run is different.
    Original soundtrack by Makeup & Vanity Set
